data.description: This remarkable 6 bedroom, single story Spanish style home has three full bathrooms and a six car garage!  It is situated on a level 3/4 of an acre lot in southwest Ukiah.  The formal dining room area could easily be repurposed into a bedroom, making this a 7 bedroom compound.  The pool is located in the courtyard with easy accessibility from any area of the house. A spectacular property and a rare find in Ukiah.  This estate will comfortably accommodate a large family or support multi-generational living.
